This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, Primary objective:, 1. To quantify the long-term effects of specific first-line antihypertensive drug therapy on morbidity and mortality in patients with hypertension., Secondary objectives:, 2. To quantify the long-term effects of high and low dose thiazides as first line therapy., 3. To quantify the blood pressure lowering efficacy according to the specific first-line therapy in the same trials., 4. To quantify drop-outs due to adverse events according to the specific first-line therapy in the same trials